{"tid":1178273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超6點45分開記者會","createTime":"2019-05-30T09:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T05:04:01.000Z","uid":117200,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"94508af70951ad31498fa8c235d3f73fe161cb4a","tid":1178273,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:42:39.000Z","msg":"消息指，政府已接納建制派今日（30日）就修訂《逃犯條例》內容提出的兩項建議。<br />\n<br />\n建制派昨晚（29日）向保安局局長李家超提交39名建制派議員的聯署信件，就修訂《逃犯條例》內容，促請政府考慮增加兩項額外措施，包括把可移交的罪行刑罰年期提高至7年或以上，以反映條例草案處理的「特別移交安排」只針對情況嚴重的罪行；以及當各地申請以個案移交的當局，應屬中央機關或部門，以內地為例，必須統一經由國家級部委，例如最高人民檢察院提出移交要求。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超將於傍晚6時45分，在政總西翼大堂會見傳媒。<br />\n<img src=\"http://theowl.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IMG_5362-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftheowl.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FIMG_5362-1024x576.jpg&h=44ce3273&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04e4d502ea818512fc4514e5db116b36e802c4c1","tid":1178273,"uid":74058,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好局長"},{"pid":"8ae8a5823a65b6b300824674b8a5c11bdf5b0507","tid":1178273,"uid":160051,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"好嬲囉，而家香港變了經濟罪犯天堂咩<br />\n係就應該冚家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4ea728e64c76dde1717acdd36635f229123af3","tid":1178273,"uid":80666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:44:27.000Z","msg":"建制派就聽"},{"pid":"de08323996ec915e530b395cb803a43b93c5c0bf","tid":1178273,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"張相入面嘅佢成個公公咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as